----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

nodemon - you do not have to restart the server every time you make changes in the node application

---> npm install nodemon -g
-g is for installing globally

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Validation for forms

1) you can do it manually
2) bunch of modules that you can use (express-validator)

https://github.com/express-validator/express-validator

---> npm install express-valdator --save

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Using MongoDB with Express JS

use a simple library ---> mongojs

https://github.com/mafintosh/mongojs

---> npm install mongojs --save

